text: Praise Tonha (born 29 March 1995) is a Zimbabwean footballer who plays as a defender for CAPS United F.C. and the Zimbabwe national football team. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:How Mine F.C. players Category:CAPS United players Category:Zimbabwe Premier Soccer League players Category:Zimbabwean footballers Category:Zimbabwe international footballers Category:Association football defenders
